{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Vestra{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<body class="body-first-step">
    <main class="main-first-step">
    
        <div id="text-first">
        <h1>WELCOME</h1>

        <div class="p-of-first">
        <p>Welcome to Vestra – The Creative Platform for Showcasing Your Talent
        At Vestra, our goal is clear: to provide a space where everyone can showcase their projects and connect with new opportunities. <br> 
        Every idea deserves to be shared and supported, and that’s why we created this platform where you can express your creativity, discover other talents, and receive valuable feedback from an engaged community. </p>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>Key Features to Promote Your Work </p>
        </div>
        <p>1.Create or Log In Easily <br>
        Get started in just a few simple steps to share your projects and interact with the community. </p>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>2.Share Your Vision <br>
        Post images, videos, or updates to showcase your projects and ideas to an enthusiastic audience. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>3.Follow, Chat, and Connect <br>
        Build relationships with other creators, exchange ideas, and find inspiration through direct conversations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>4.Engage with Votes and Comments <br>
        Receive votes and comments on your projects — the more you get, the more visibility your project gains. Share your ideas and support others’! </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>5.Direct Sharing on Your Profile <br>
        With just a click, add inspiring content directly to your profile and share it easily with your network. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>6.Discover Easily with an Intelligent Algorithm <br>
        Our system provides personalized project suggestions based on your interests and preferences.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>7.Weekly Top Project Rankings <br>
        Every week, the projects with the most votes are highlighted in their category. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>8.Special Events with Votes from Professionals <br>
        Participate in events where professionals can vote for their favorite projects. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>9.A Dynamic Homepage to Inspire You <br>
        Discover the most popular projects right when you land on the site. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>10.Two Communities in One Place <br>
        Vestra is divided into two main sections: creators sharing their work, and those seeking new inspiration and opportunities. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>11.Certification for Opportunity Creators <br>
        Professionals can validate their credibility with an official certification of reliability. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>12.Complete and Customizable Profiles <br>
        Build a unique profile with your projects, a personal description, a goal, and a space to interact with your network. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>13.Integrated Notifications to Stay Updated <br>
        Get notified of every interaction with your posts and projects. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>14.Powerful Search Bar to Find What You’re Looking For <br>
        Easily find talents, projects, or groups with our efficient search feature. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>15.Create and Join Collaborative Groups <br>
        Start or join group projects and exchange ideas with other members. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="separe">
        <p>A Strong Commitment to the Community <br>
        Vestra isn’t just a website — it’s a dynamic network where talents thrive and projects come to life. <br>
        Join us and make your ideas shine. Let’s celebrate creativity together and give visibility to projects that truly deserve it!
        </p>

        </div>

        </div>

        <h2> <strong>Are you ready?</strong></h2>
        
        <a href="{{ path('app_projects') }}"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Let's GO!</button></a>

        
        

        
        
        </div>
    </main>
    
</body>


